genresAdvancedInfo.name: luxembourgian hip hop
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Luxembourgian hip hop is a genre that combines the raw energy of hip hop with the melodic sensibilities of Luxembourgian music. It is characterized by its socially conscious lyrics, intricate rhymes, and powerful beats, and has become a powerful voice for the country's youth culture.
